div.h2: urls + outbox Table Schema and Index Layout

ul.li: TEXT: variable-length; toasted if original_url > 2 kB
TIMESTAMPTZ: UTC int64 microseconds since epoch (8 B)
BOOLEAN: 1 byte; PostgreSQL aligns to 8-byte boundary
event_type: routing key string (~12 chars avg)
published_at NULL = not yet published (partial index target)
Estimated row size: ~650 B average (JSONB dominant)

p.strong: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX idx_urls_short_code ON urls(short_code)

div.p:
B-Tree Root Page
Key type : VARCHAR(10) Height: ~23 Fill: 90%
Internal Node Internal Node [0000000 mZZZZZZ] [n000000 ZZZZZZZ]
Leaf Pages (ctidheap) Leaf Pages (ctidheap)
Queries using this index FindByCode redirect hot path sql SELECT ... FROM urls WHERE short_code = $1
Collision detection during INSERT Cache key derivation (Redis = "url:" + short_code)

p.strong: CREATE INDEX idx_urls_user_id_created ON urls(user_id, created_at DESC)

div.p:
B-Tree Root Page
Key: (user_id UUID, created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DESC) Height: ~34 Fill: 85% Sort: ASC user_id, DESC time
Internal Internal Internal (uid=A, t=T3) (uid=M, t=T2) (uid=Z, t=T1)
Queries using this index ListByUser first page (no cursor) sql SELECT ... FROM urls WHERE user_id = $1 ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 21
ListByUser subsequent pages (keyset cursor) sql WHERE user_id = $1 AND (created_at, id) < ($2, $3)

p.strong: CREATE INDEX idx_outbox_unpublished ON outbox(created_at ASC) WHERE published_at IS NULL

div.p:
Partial B-Tree (published_at IS NULL)
Key: created_at TIMESTAMPTZ ASC Predicate check logic
Leaf Page (oldest) Leaf Page (recent)
Queries using this index FetchUnpublished Poller (every 2s) sql SELECT ... FROM outbox WHERE published_at IS NULL ORDER BY created_at ASC
MarkPublished Side effect: row drops OUT of partial index
